_urgent" value="1"> Acil Satış</label><label>Öne Çıkarma Süresi<select name="featured_days"><option value="0">Yok</option><?php foreach($packages as $p): ?><option value="<?= (int)$p['days'] ?>"><?= e($p['name']) ?> - <?= number_format((float)$p['price'],2,',','.') ?> <?= e($p['currency']) ?></option><?php endforeach; ?></select></label><label class="full">Açıklama<textarea name="description" rows="3"></textarea></label><button class="ao-btn">İlanı Kaydet</button></form></div>
